OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Top executives of major Western oil    
OL,6, companies are to testify before the US 
OL,7, Congress amid accusations that they    
OL,8, misled the public about climate change.
OL,10,FDemocrat lawmakers say the hearings    
OL,11,Fwill focus on the industry's           
OL,12,Fdecades-long denial of its products'   
OL,13,Fleading role in fuelling climate       
OL,14,Fchange.                                
OL,16,FThe companies said they hoped to use   
OL,17,Fthe hearings to highlight recent       
OL,18,Fefforts to address climate change.     
OL,20,FThis comes just days before the start  
OL,21,Fof the UN's COP26 climate conference.  
